<HEADER>
A9845 &Cx1f; tad-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NEWS-QUESTIONS04-TAKE     02-03 1525
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NEWS-QUESTIONS04-TAKE1-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    EDITORS: THIS IS PART ONE OF A TWO PART FILE
