<P>
   TAE-BO _ Tae-Bo's like boxing, but there are no gloves. It's
also like karate, but there are no opponents (unless you mistakenly
TKO the poor schmuck next to you). Slip in some hip-hop tunes, and
behold! Your class roster includes Pamela Anderson, Paula Abdul,
Brooke Shields and Neve Campbell. Even the prince of the puck,
Wayne Gretzky, and hoopster Shaquille O'Neal. And, oh, don't forget
Queen Latifah, Ashley Judd and comic Sinbad. Billy Blanks, however,
isn't one to drop names. He'd rather we drop our elbows to our
waists during the uppercut punches. ``Your waist,'' he yells, ``is
your shock absorber.'' My waist, kind sir, is my chocolate
absorber. (Grantham, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
