</P>
<P>
   RECIPES --
</P>
<P>
   CYBERSPICE -- While surfing the Web, we came across the
fascinating world of Renaissance, medieval and ancient cookery. We
soon learned that this subject has a loyal following of scholarly
souls, serious researchers, food historians, dedicated foodies,
chefs and the plain curious. (Parham, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   NUTRITION -- For many, the Bible offers a place to seek comfort,
understanding and spiritual healing. For Lee Holtzman, it also
