</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-AARP _ WASHINGTON _ President Clinton addresses the AARP
on his Social Security and Medicare proposals. (Lipman, Cox News
Service).
</P>
<P>
   IMPEACH-BAXTER _ Is this the final chapter of the impechment
