   Price: $139.99 ($19.99 for cartridge)
</P>
<P>
   Pros: Can play on several systems; soft grip around the wheel;
great pedals.
</P>
<P>
   Cons: Some gamers report imprecise effects while playing racing
games. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
