</P>
<P>
   Platform: PC
</P>
<P>
   Price: $100
</P>
<P>
   Pros: Inexpensive; works with DOS; accepts optional rudder and
throttle controls on flight simulator programs.
</P>
<P>
   Cons: Doesn't always work with latest games; no support for
faster USB port connector. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
