   Dual Shock Analog Controller
</P>
<P>
   Company: Sony
</P>
<P>
   Platform: Playstation
</P>
<P>
   Price: $30
</P>
<P>
   Pros: Dual precision controllers feel good under the thumbs; no
batteries required.
</P>
<P>
   Cons: Video gamepad force feedback hardly simulates the real
thing. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
