<P>
   IMPEACH-RPD (Washington) _ With the impeachment trial of
President Clinton set to reconvene Thursday, House prosecutors on
Wednesday questioned the last of three witnesses behind closed
doors and began a final drive to bring Monica Lewinsky and two
Clinton advisers to testify in person before the Senate. By Alison
Mitchell. With photo.
</P>
