<HEADER>
A0815 &Cx1f; tad-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OLY-SURVEY04-COX     02-03 1443
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-OLY-SURVEY04-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Public `disgusted' with Olympics, survey shows
 &HT;    By Melissa Turner
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
