<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 
 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    PHONING HOME. A host of telecom companies are investing billions
of dollars in Mexico to offer local phone service, but not all of
them will survive.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-MEXICO:TELECOM-LATINTRADE-NYTSF.
 &HT;    
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased _ the rate is not
