established in Gaza City. Mrs. Arafat, 35, would seem an unlikely
life partner for the 69-year old Palestinian revolutionary who
remains forever wedded to his cause. But in ideology Mrs. Arafat,
whose husband is to meet on Thursday with President Clinton in
Washington, is every bit the fiery Palestinian freedom
fighter.(Rina Castelnuovo/New York Times Photo)
